snippet.title: Go Slimey Go! | Latin American Games Showcase TGA 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
Go Slimey Go!
A heartwarming platformer where you guide Slimey, the realm’s weakest yet most adorable creature, on a journey to visit his friends for a drink. Use simple controls to explore challenging and whimsical levels, filled with surprises along the way.
